## 二、引号使用规范

### JS 字符串：单引号

```javascript
const name = 'Alice'    // ✅
const name = "Alice"    // ❌
```

### JS 模板字符串：反引号 + `${变量}`

```javascript
const greeting = `Hello, ${name}!`              // ✅
const path = '/api/user/' + userId + '/detail'  // ❌
```

### Vue 模板：标签属性用双引号

```vue
<div class="page" id="main"></div>    <!-- ✅ -->
<div class='page'></div>              <!-- ❌ -->
```

### 动态类名：单引号包裹

```vue
<div :class="'page'"></div>
<div :class="isActive ? 'tab tab--active' : 'tab'"></div>
```

### Less/CSS：BEM + kebab-case

```less
.page { }            // Block
.page__header { }    // Element
.page--dark { }      // Modifier
```

